attributeSource.infoString2: Better Homes and Gardens Gary Greene

data.description: Great family home with lots of storage and oversized backyard that includes newly installed privacy fence. Large country kitchen and walk-in pantry. Beautiful wood laminate and ceramic tile throughout the home.  Fabulous bonus room in garage/storage building that is fully finished and air-conditioned that could be used as an extra office or man-cave. Must see this home to appreciate it's full potential!
